title: Leaders of Catalonia independence bid on trial in Madrid
description:
The trial of the leaders of the failed attempt to declare Catalonia’s independence from Spain is underway in Madrid. Twelve “separatist” leaders were accused of instigating and organizing the insurgency, as well as the misuse of public funds. Pro-independence protesters briefly blocked highways and roads in the Spanish city of Barcelona. RT’s Yulia Shapovalova has the story for News.Views.Hughes.
